      "para_id": "Q001081.6",
      "line_range": "6",
      "translation": "(ii 1') ... assigned ... to Lugal-Urubaś šourtyard as regular offering . En-ana-tum ... for Ama-ĝeštin-ana ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001081.12",
      "line_range": "12",
      "translation": "(iii 1') He had them/it bring healthy goats and healthy kids . He had them/it bring healthy cows and healthy calves . He ... swift donkey stallions with breeding she-asses ."
    }
  ],
